I had the oportunity to watch the fist ep again of BBB, I find Jirou criptic; the vampire tragic hero seems hard and quite vicious but the softness of heart that he shows later in the show contradicts any expectation I ever had with his development. At first I though of him as a bad copy of Alucard from Hellsing (one of my favorite vampire anime) but then after finishing the 13 eps I found myself liking Jirou for his hidden kindness and rare humanity, something that you wouldnt find in a hard core vampire. I have a few screenshots of Jirou and his coffin, and I'll be working on a wallpaper and perhaps a signature for the roleplaying website I joined, here are the ones I like the most, help me pick :P

Yeah, there is a first time for everything and this is my first time here although I do have other LJs I recently developed an interest in LJ comunities so <<;; here I am  

I hope I make a lot of friends and reach my goals, Im going to be posting pics, GFXing and stuff, Im always doing something so this is going to be crowded in a while ^.^ v
